ŁIn Memory of Lilian Dorothy Timmins
7th September 1927 - 4th September 2011
"The memories and love, I leave behind
are yours to keep. I have found my rest,
turned my face to the sun and now I sleep."
Till we meet again mom, love Jacqueline X
